mplex in which NS1A(1-73) sits astride the minor groove of A-form RNA with a few amino acids in the helix 2-helix 2' face forming an electrostatically stabilized interaction with the phosphodiester backbone. This mode of dsRNA binding differs from that observed for any other dsRNA-binding protein.},
